% B6b with stack recording disabled.
% B6b - B6b_norec = cost of estack toArray() at this depth, plus
% the constant per-error ostack/dstack copy. Compare delta against
% (B6 - B6_norec) to isolate the depth-scaling component.
errordict /recordstacks false put
/d4 { /test /Bench raiseerror } def
/d3 { d4 } def
/d2 { d3 } def
/d1 { d2 } def
tic 1000000 { { d1 } stopped { handleerror } if } repeat toc ==
quit
